description: Doe-eyed Tannor Reed makes his Next Door premiere in what is sure to be the first of many scenes, that is unless Scott Finn breaks him first. Luckily Scott has promised not to go too hard on Tannor's first go-round, but that doesn't mean he's not as hard as can be. As Scott says, 'I'm in Heaven right now,' and a quick glance at Tannor looking up at you makes it easy to see why. But Tannor isn't just a pretty face. He's ready for a good fuck and just as hot for Scott's body. It all makes for a steamy first time out, and a memorable introduction, indeed.Enjoy!
title: Breaking Tannor
